Include CoreFoundation/CoreFoundation.h (#2364)

* Include CoreFoundation/CoreFoundation.h

This is correct, since this file does use CoreFoundation types, and it
is necessary because on old macOS versions IOKit/ps/IOPowerSources.h,
which is already included and which also uses CoreFoundation types,
forgot to include CoreFoundation/CoreFoundation.h.

Fixes #2362

Include net/if.h before net/if_dl.h (#2361)

In old versions of macOS, net/if_dl.h neglects to include sys/types.h,
which results in build failure:

error: unknown type name 'u_char'; did you mean 'char'?

Including net/if.h first works around the problem because net/if.h
includes sys/types.h.

Fixes #2360
